WEBVTT

00:02.502 --> 00:03.878
-<i> HOT IN CLEVELAND</i>
IS RECORDED IN FRONT OF

00:03.961 --> 00:05.964
A LIVE STUDIO AUDIENCE.

00:06.047 --> 00:08.258
- [frustrated scream]

00:08.341 --> 00:10.593
- IS VICTORIA
TRYING TO IRON AGAIN?

00:10.677 --> 00:13.430
- NO, SHE'S READING HER DAUGHTER
EMMY'S LATEST REWRITE

00:13.513 --> 00:14.556
OF THEIR LIFETIME MOVIE.

00:14.639 --> 00:15.765
- OH.

00:15.849 --> 00:18.226
- THIS SCRIPT
IS A MONSTROSITY.

00:18.309 --> 00:20.437
EMMY'S REWRITE MAKES ME
COME OFF AS SOME SORT OF

00:20.520 --> 00:22.939
DERANGED <i> MOMMIE DEAREST.</i>

00:23.022 --> 00:25.775
THIS MOVIE WAS SUPPOSED
TO BE MY COMEBACK VEHICLE,

00:25.859 --> 00:29.279
BUT IF I MAKE THIS MOVIE,
I'LL BE A PARIAH IN THIS TOWN.

00:29.362 --> 00:31.281
WELL...
MAYBE NOT IN THIS TOWN,

00:31.364 --> 00:32.573
BUT, YOU KNOW,
IN TOWNS THAT MATTER,

00:32.656 --> 00:34.284
LIKE L.A. AND NEW YORK.

00:34.367 --> 00:36.953
- CLEVELAND
IS VERY FORGIVING.

00:37.036 --> 00:40.457
IT'S LIKE THE ELASTIC WAISTBAND
OF AMERICAN CITIES.

00:40.540 --> 00:42.500
- IT'S <i> TOO</i> FORGIVING.

00:42.584 --> 00:43.918
- NOT THIS AGAIN.

00:44.002 --> 00:46.337
SHE KEEPS NATTERING ON
ABOUT SOME CAVALIER BARON

00:46.421 --> 00:47.964
USURPING KING JAMES.

00:48.047 --> 00:51.426
- BARON DAVIS!
POINT GUARD FOR THE CAVS.

00:51.509 --> 00:56.264
- SEE? SHE'S JUST STRINGING
RANDOM WORDS TOGETHER.

00:56.347 --> 00:58.808
- OH, THANK GOD
YOU GUYS ARE HERE.

00:58.892 --> 01:00.310
I'VE HAD THE WORST DAY.

01:00.393 --> 01:01.978
- SORRY,
BUT IF YOU WANT TO VENT,

01:02.061 --> 01:03.813
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO TAKE
A NUMBER AND WAIT YOUR TURN.

01:03.897 --> 01:05.522
- I'VE BEEN BIKINI SHOPPING.

01:05.607 --> 01:07.150
- ALONE?
- OH, DEAR GOD!

01:07.233 --> 01:09.277
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?

01:09.360 --> 01:10.820
- BIKINI SHOPPING
IS A MINEFIELD.

01:10.904 --> 01:14.532
ONE WRONG THONG
AND YOU'RE A SUMO WRESTLER.

01:14.616 --> 01:18.161
- ONE WRONG TOP
AND YOU'RE A TEN-YEAR-OLD BOY.

01:18.244 --> 01:20.330
- ONE WRONG
BATHING SUIT SKIRT

01:20.413 --> 01:23.458
AND YOU'RE THE HIPPO
FROM <i> FANTASIA.</i>

01:23.541 --> 01:26.544
- WHY TORTURE YOURSELF NOW?
SUMMER'S MONTHS AWAY.

01:26.628 --> 01:28.171
- I'M GOING
TO BERMUDA NEXT WEEK.

01:28.254 --> 01:30.465
<i>WOMAN'S DAY MAGAZINE</i>
ASKED ME TO SPEAK AT A SEMINAR,

01:30.548 --> 01:33.176
AND THEY'RE HAVING IT AT THIS
FABULOUS HOTEL ON THE BEACH.

01:33.259 --> 01:35.220
- WOMEN ONLY?
OH, DEAR.

01:35.303 --> 01:38.014
MEN NEVER LOOK PAST LEGS
AND CLEAVAGE, BUT WOMEN...

01:38.097 --> 01:41.851
- OH, YOU'LL BE JUDGED
MERCILESSLY.

01:41.935 --> 01:44.896
I'M JUDGING YOU RIGHT NOW.

01:44.979 --> 01:46.356
- I KNOW.

01:46.439 --> 01:48.191
THAT'S WHY I NARROWED IT DOWN
TO THREE SUITS.

01:48.274 --> 01:51.069
IF I CAN LOSE ENOUGH WEIGHT
TO FIT INTO THIS,

01:51.152 --> 01:53.154
THEY'LL SAY,
"SHE LOOKS GREAT."

01:53.238 --> 01:55.740
BUT IF I CAN STARVE MYSELF
INTO THIS, THEY'LL SAY,

01:55.824 --> 01:57.700
"HAS SHE HAD WORK DONE?"

01:57.784 --> 02:01.913
BUT IF I CAN DEHYDRATE MYSELF
INTO THIS, THEY'LL SAY,

02:01.996 --> 02:04.666
"OH, MY GOD,
I HATE HER."

02:04.749 --> 02:07.794
I JUST WANT THEM
TO HATE ME SO MUCH.

02:07.877 --> 02:10.880
[doorbell rings]

02:10.964 --> 02:14.384
- OH, WHAT A SURPRISE.
FLOWERS.

02:14.467 --> 02:17.554
- VICTORIA, DID YOU SEND
YOURSELF FLOWERS AGAIN?

02:17.637 --> 02:19.055
- YES. I HAD TO.

02:19.138 --> 02:21.349
I WAS THAT UPSET
ABOUT THAT SCRIPT.

02:21.432 --> 02:23.226
- ACTUALLY,
THEY'RE FROM ME.

02:23.309 --> 02:27.230
- WAIT,
I KNOW THAT VOICE.

02:27.313 --> 02:28.231
[gasps]

02:28.314 --> 02:30.108
- HELLO, VICTORIA.

02:30.191 --> 02:32.735
- LUCCI!

02:32.819 --> 02:35.530
[ominous soap opera music]

02:35.613 --> 02:37.949
♪ ♪

02:38.032 --> 02:43.413
- I'VE BEEN EXPERIMENTING
WITH NEW RINGTONES.

02:43.496 --> 02:46.249
HELLO?

02:55.300 --> 02:57.802
{\an8}THIS IS SO EXCITING!

02:57.886 --> 03:01.598
{\an8}WE'VE NEVER HAD A BIG STAR
IN THE HOUSE BEFORE!

03:01.681 --> 03:04.475
{\an8}- I'M BIG, ELKA.
- WELL, SURE.

03:04.559 --> 03:07.478
{\an8}COMPARED TO HER,
YOU'RE A MOOSE!

03:10.023 --> 03:12.108
{\an8}- HI, I'M MELANIE.
- N-N-N-NO.

03:12.191 --> 03:14.777
{\an8}NO INTRODUCTIONS.
SHE'S NOT STAYING.

03:14.861 --> 03:16.154
{\an8}- VICTORIA, PLEASE.

03:16.237 --> 03:18.114
{\an8}WHEN <i> ALL MY CHILDREN</i>
WAS CANCELED,

03:18.197 --> 03:20.617
{\an8}I HAD NOWHERE TO TURN.

03:20.700 --> 03:25.747
{\an8}I WAS CURLED UP IN MY
JEWELRY CLOSET, HOPING TO DIE.

03:25.830 --> 03:27.457
{\an8}AND SUDDENLY,
I REMEMBERED.

03:27.540 --> 03:31.252
{\an8}WHEN YOUR SOAP CAREER IMPLODED,
YOU CAME HERE, TO CLEVELAND,

03:31.336 --> 03:34.464
{\an8}TO FIND SOLACE
AMONG THE LITTLE PEOPLE.

03:34.547 --> 03:36.466
{\an8}- OH, PLEASE.
NO ONE'S LITTLER THAN YOU.

03:36.549 --> 03:41.512
{\an8}IF I POPPED YOUR HEAD BACK,
A PEZ WOULD FLY OUT.

03:43.723 --> 03:45.767
{\an8}- PLEASE, VICTORIA,
DON'T TURN ME OUT.

03:45.850 --> 03:48.019
{\an8}THIS IS THE LOWEST POINT
OF MY LIFE.

03:48.102 --> 03:50.605
{\an8}- OH, BOO-HOO!

03:50.688 --> 03:54.442
{\an8}I AM NOT HAVING 92 POUNDS
OF PURE EVIL UNDER THIS ROOF.

03:54.525 --> 03:58.780
{\an8}- 90! I LOST 2 POUNDS
FROM STRESS.

03:58.863 --> 04:00.573
{\an8}- STRESS!
THAT'S WHAT I NEED!

04:00.657 --> 04:02.700
{\an8}NO, I'M A STRESS EATER!
I DON'T NEED STRESS.

04:02.784 --> 04:05.495
{\an8}NOW I'M STRESSING ABOUT STRESS!
DO WE HAVE ANY COOKIES?

04:05.578 --> 04:07.956
{\an8}- OH, COME ON, VICTORIA.

04:08.039 --> 04:11.167
{\an8}SHE'S SO CUTE.
CAN'T WE KEEP HER?

04:13.336 --> 04:15.546
{\an8}- YOU TWO NEED TO
TALK THIS OUT IN PRIVATE.

04:15.630 --> 04:17.632
{\an8}CAN SOMEONE SHOW ME
TO MY DRESSING ROOM?

04:17.714 --> 04:21.052
{\an8}- THIS IS A HOUSE.
WE DON'T HAVE DRESSING ROOMS.

04:21.135 --> 04:25.932
{\an8}- OH, GOD,
I'LL NEVER SURVIVE IN THE WILD.

04:29.769 --> 04:32.647
- ALLOW ME.

04:32.730 --> 04:34.023
- WHERE DID YOU GET THAT?

04:34.107 --> 04:38.861
- IT WAS MADE
FOR ME BY NASA.

04:38.945 --> 04:42.657
NATIONAL ASSOCIATION
OF SOAP ACTRESSES.

04:42.740 --> 04:45.535
HERE, TRY IT.
- OH.

04:45.618 --> 04:48.496
THAT'S IT!
SKYHOOK!

04:48.579 --> 04:50.873
OH, I'VE GOT TO
GET A MESSAGE TO BARON DAVIS.

04:50.957 --> 04:53.209
THE SKYHOOK IS WHAT HE NEEDS
TO UP HIS GAME!

04:53.293 --> 04:55.837
- I CAN ARRANGE THAT.
I KNOW PEOPLE.

04:55.920 --> 04:57.213
- REALLY?
- WELL, OF COURSE.

04:57.296 --> 04:59.716
I'M STILL ERICA KANE.

04:59.799 --> 05:01.342
I MEAN, SUSAN LUCCI.

05:01.426 --> 05:05.430
WAIT...NO.
THAT'S RIGHT, SUSAN LUCCI.

05:05.513 --> 05:08.933
- GOOD MORNING!
OH, WOW, WHAT'S ALL THIS?

05:09.017 --> 05:10.685
- OH, I JUST WHIPPED UP
SOME GOODIES

05:10.768 --> 05:14.022
TO THANK YOU ALL FOR TALKING
VICTORIA INTO LETTING ME STAY.

05:14.105 --> 05:16.858
- OH, THAT'S VERY SWEET,
BUT I ONLY HAVE A WEEK

05:16.941 --> 05:21.112
TO REACH MY BIKINI WEIGHT,
SO I'LL JUST SNIFF A GRAPEFRUIT.

05:21.195 --> 05:23.865
- OH, SWEETIE,
I HAVE A MIRACLE SUPPLEMENT

05:23.948 --> 05:26.075
THAT'LL MAKE YOU LOSE
10 POUNDS BY SATURDAY

05:26.159 --> 05:27.535
NO MATTER
HOW MUCH YOU EAT.

05:27.618 --> 05:31.456
- THOSE ARE THE MOST BEAUTIFUL
WORDS I'VE EVER HEARD!

05:31.539 --> 05:34.250
- BEFORE YOU ASK ME
HOW MY DATE WENT LAST NIGHT,

05:34.334 --> 05:38.254
HE CRIED ALL THE WAY THROUGH
THE CHIPMUNK MOVIE.

05:43.176 --> 05:48.306
- HERE, SAD SACK,
HAVE A MUFFIN.

05:48.389 --> 05:51.768
- I KNOW A MAN
WHO'D BE PERFECT FOR YOU.

05:51.851 --> 05:54.604
HE CONSULTED ON OUR
DOCTORS WITHOUT BORDERS EPISODE,

05:54.687 --> 05:56.439
AND NOW HE'S WITH
THE CLEVELAND CLINIC.

05:56.522 --> 05:57.982
- WHAT'S THE CATCH?

05:58.066 --> 06:00.276
- WELL, THERE IS
ONE SMALL THING.

06:00.359 --> 06:02.737
HE WON'T BE
A DOCTOR FOREVER.

06:02.820 --> 06:05.782
HE HAS THIS CRAZY NOTION OF
SOMEDAY OWNING HIS OWN WINERY.

06:05.865 --> 06:07.992
- HOW FAST
CAN YOU CALL HIM?

06:08.076 --> 06:09.285
- I CAN DO IT RIGHT NOW.

06:09.368 --> 06:11.287
AND THEN I'LL CALL
BARON DAVIS,

06:11.370 --> 06:12.830
AND THEN I'LL CALL
MY NUTRITIONIST

06:12.914 --> 06:14.248
ABOUT THAT DIET CAPSULE.

06:14.332 --> 06:16.876
- WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN
ALL OUR LIVES?

06:16.959 --> 06:19.712
- MOSTLY?
PINE VALLEY.

06:22.715 --> 06:27.845
- I'M GONNA SAY IT.
I LIKE HER BETTER THAN VICTORIA.

06:27.929 --> 06:29.764
- ELKA, WE CAN'T
LIKE HER BETTER.

06:29.847 --> 06:31.182
- BUT WE COULD
LIKE HER THE SAME.

06:31.265 --> 06:32.809
- WELL, WELL, WELL.

06:32.892 --> 06:35.978
MY SO-CALLED FRIENDS.

06:36.062 --> 06:39.315
USUALLY, WHEN I EAVESDROP
FROM THE BACK STAIRS

06:39.398 --> 06:42.693
I GET NOTHING,
BUT NOT TODAY!

06:42.777 --> 06:45.029
NOW, DON'T YOU SEE THAT
SHE'S ONLY BEING NICE TO YOU

06:45.113 --> 06:47.573
TO FURTHER SOME EVIL PLAN
TO DESTROY ME?

06:47.657 --> 06:50.618
- YOU KNOW, IT IS POSSIBLE
THERE IS NO EVIL PLAN.

06:50.701 --> 06:53.496
- OH, PLEASE, THIS IS
SUSAN LUCCI WE'RE TALKING ABOUT.

06:53.579 --> 06:56.958
UGH! I HAVE PUT UP WITH
DECADES OF ABUSE FROM HER.

06:57.041 --> 06:59.418
YOU REMEMBER THE YEAR
THAT SHE SNUCK MY PICTURE

06:59.502 --> 07:04.048
INTO THE "IN MEMORIAM"
SECTION OF THE EMMYS?

07:06.092 --> 07:09.846
UNLIKE YOU,
I INTEND TO BE VIGILANT.

07:09.929 --> 07:14.350
AS GOD AS MY WITNESS,
I WILL NEVER BE LUCCI'D AGAIN.

07:14.433 --> 07:17.979
[soap opera music]

07:18.062 --> 07:22.733
- OH, I GOT A VOICEMAIL!

07:22.817 --> 07:25.695
- THANK YOU SO MUCH,
SHE'LL BE THRILLED.

07:25.778 --> 07:29.031
OH!
GOOD MORNING, VICTORIA.

07:29.115 --> 07:30.408
DON'T YOU
LOOK LOVELY TODAY.

07:30.491 --> 07:33.578
- OH, YOU'RE GOOD, LUCCI.

07:33.661 --> 07:36.330
THAT ALMOST SOUNDED SINCERE.

07:36.414 --> 07:38.833
LIKE ERICA KANE
WHEN SHE IMPERSONATED A NUN

07:38.916 --> 07:42.837
TO AVOID ARREST
FOR THE MURDER OF KENT BOGARD.

07:42.920 --> 07:45.006
- OR MAYBE
YOU'RE JUST BEING PARANOID,

07:45.089 --> 07:47.216
LIKE HONOR ST. RAVEN
WHEN SHE THOUGHT HER KITTEN

07:47.300 --> 07:50.219
WAS TRYING
TO READ HER MIND.

07:50.303 --> 07:52.763
- BUT YOU FORGET
THAT THEY FOUND A TRANSMITTER

07:52.847 --> 07:55.850
IN BUTTERCUP'S BRAIN,

07:55.933 --> 07:58.186
SO I WASN'T WRONG THEN,
AND I'M NOT WRONG NOW.

07:58.269 --> 08:01.355
NO, THE REAL YOU
IS JUST BENEATH THE SURFACE,

08:01.439 --> 08:05.193
BARELY CONCEALED
BY ALL THAT CONCEALER.

08:05.276 --> 08:07.904
- THIS IS
THE REAL ME, VICTORIA.

08:07.987 --> 08:09.363
THE NEW ME.

08:09.447 --> 08:11.908
ALL I WANT IS A CHANCE
TO PROVE IT TO YOU,

08:11.991 --> 08:14.702
LIKE HONOR ST. RAVEN
PROVED THE EXISTENCE

08:14.785 --> 08:17.246
OF THAT WHOLE
PARALLEL UNIVERSE.

08:17.330 --> 08:19.582
- WELL, IN THAT UNIVERSE,
AS IN THIS ONE,

08:19.665 --> 08:21.584
I HAVE EYES
IN THE BACK OF MY HEAD,

08:21.667 --> 08:26.214
AND THEY
WILL BE WATCHING YOU.

08:29.842 --> 08:31.719
- EXCUSE ME, ELKA?

08:31.802 --> 08:35.597
- BARON DAVIS?
IT'S REALLY YOU?

08:35.681 --> 08:37.433
- YEAH, SUSAN SENT ME.

08:37.515 --> 08:39.143
I HEAR YOU'RE SOME KIND OF
SPORTS WHISPERER?

08:39.227 --> 08:41.604
- YES.

08:41.687 --> 08:43.981
SIT DOWN.

08:44.065 --> 08:46.776
LOOK, YOU'VE GOT
SOME GREAT SKILLS.

08:46.859 --> 08:49.403
- WELL, THANK YOU.

08:49.487 --> 08:54.242
- I HAVE AN IDEA THAT CAN
TAKE YOU TO THE NEXT LEVEL.

08:55.493 --> 08:57.161
- UM...

08:57.245 --> 08:59.121
I THINK THAT'S AGAINST
LEAGUE REGULATIONS.

08:59.205 --> 09:00.122
- NO, NO!

09:00.206 --> 09:04.043
I WANT YOU TO BRING BACK
KAREEM'S SKYHOOK.

09:06.337 --> 09:09.257
- NO DISRESPECT,
BUT KAREEM'S A LEGEND.

09:09.340 --> 09:12.468
AND THE SKYHOOK?
THAT'S HIS TRADEMARK.

09:12.551 --> 09:14.428
- WELL,
NOW IT CAN BE YOURS!

09:14.512 --> 09:16.264
- I HAVE MY OWN TRADEMARK.

09:16.347 --> 09:18.683
MY BEARD HAS ITS OWN
TWITTER FOLLOWING.

09:21.560 --> 09:24.272
- DOES YOUR BEARD
HAVE AN ENDORSEMENT DEAL

09:24.355 --> 09:26.816
OR DATE A KARDASHIAN?

09:26.899 --> 09:30.653
- GIVE ME THAT THING.

09:30.736 --> 09:33.531
- YOU'RE GONNA LOVE JOY.
SHE'S A LEGGY BRITISH BOMBSHELL.

09:33.614 --> 09:34.532
- REALLY?

09:34.615 --> 09:37.159
WHEN THE ESCORT SERVICE
SAID THAT SUSAN LUCCI

09:37.243 --> 09:38.828
WAS HIRING ME
TO SEDUCE SOMEONE,

09:38.911 --> 09:41.664
I JUST ASSUMED IT WAS SOME SKANK
YOU WANTED TO GET EVEN WITH.

09:41.747 --> 09:45.668
- YOU'RE CONFUSING ME
WITH ERICA KANE.

09:45.751 --> 09:47.336
I HAVE ONLY
THE PUREST MOTIVATION.

09:47.420 --> 09:50.673
JUST CASH LOVINGLY
EXCHANGED FOR SEX.

09:50.756 --> 09:52.383
- ONLY SEX?

09:52.466 --> 09:54.343
YOU PAID FOR THE FULL
BOYFRIEND EXPERIENCE.

09:54.427 --> 09:55.511
- OH, ABSOLUTELY.

09:55.594 --> 09:58.556
I WANT HER TO KNOW THAT MEN
CAN BE DECENT AND HONEST.

09:58.639 --> 10:01.434
DID YOU MEMORIZE
YOUR FAKE BACKSTORY?

10:01.517 --> 10:04.186
- YES, I AM A WINE-LOVING,
COMMITMENT-SEEKING,

10:04.270 --> 10:07.606
DOCTOR WITHOUT BOUNDARIES.
- WITHOUT <i> BORDERS.</i>

10:09.108 --> 10:11.736
OH, THERE SHE IS!
JOY, SWEETIE!

10:11.819 --> 10:14.488
JOY, THIS IS
DR. DAVID GETHERS.

10:14.572 --> 10:16.365
DAVID,
THIS IS JOY SCROGGS.

10:16.449 --> 10:18.701
- I HOPE I'M JUST
FASHIONABLY LATE.

10:18.784 --> 10:20.620
- I'D SAY GORGEOUSLY LATE,

10:20.703 --> 10:22.204
AND DEFINITELY
WORTH WAITING FOR.

10:22.288 --> 10:25.916
- WELL, DOCTOR, DON'T YOU HAVE
A LOVELY BAR-SIDE MANNER.

10:26.000 --> 10:28.044
- OH, I JUST LOVE A STORY

10:28.127 --> 10:30.755
THAT'S GUARANTEED
TO HAVE A HAPPY ENDING.

10:40.639 --> 10:42.016
- MMM.

10:42.099 --> 10:44.226
- DAMN IT!
SHE'S NOT RUNNING FROM THE LAW,

10:44.310 --> 10:46.562
SHE DOESN'T NEED
AN ORGAN TRANSPLANT,

10:46.645 --> 10:47.730
AND IT TURNS OUT
THAT ALL THAT STUFF

10:47.813 --> 10:50.733
ABOUT HER BEING IN SOME
SATANIC CULT WAS JUST A RUMOR

10:50.816 --> 10:54.445
THAT I'M NOW REMEMBERING
I STARTED.

10:54.528 --> 10:57.073
- PEOPLE CAN CHANGE.

10:57.156 --> 10:59.408
THANKS TO HER SUPPLEMENT,
I'VE LOST 5 POUNDS!

10:59.492 --> 11:02.703
I HAVEN'T BEEN THIS HAPPY
SINCE THE STOMACH FLU OF '94,

11:02.787 --> 11:04.246
WHEN I DROPPED
TWO JEAN SIZES

11:04.330 --> 11:06.916
IN THREE WONDERFULLY
HORRIFYING DAYS.

11:08.668 --> 11:12.338
- BARON DAVIS SKYHOOKED
THE CAVS TO ANOTHER WIN!

11:12.421 --> 11:15.299
I LOVE LUCCI!

11:17.343 --> 11:18.594
- WOW.

11:18.677 --> 11:20.388
SOMEONE'S DRESSED
TO SAY YES.

11:20.471 --> 11:24.266
- I ALREADY SAID YES.
LAST NIGHT.

11:24.350 --> 11:27.895
I'VE NEVER BEEN WITH A MAN
WHO'S SO EAGER TO PLEASE.

11:27.978 --> 11:29.939
"IS IT BETTER LIKE THIS
OR LIKE THIS?

11:30.022 --> 11:32.149
LIKE THIS OR LIKE THIS?"

11:32.233 --> 11:35.319
IT WAS LIKE THE PORN VERSION
OF AN EYE EXAM.

11:37.405 --> 11:39.240
I'M OFF TO MEET HIM NOW.

11:39.323 --> 11:41.450
- HEY, ELKA AND I
ARE GONNA GO

11:41.534 --> 11:42.910
FOR SOME BIG,
GOOEY CHEESEBURGERS.

11:42.993 --> 11:45.830
YOU WANT TO JOIN US?
- NO, I CAN'T EAT.

11:45.913 --> 11:49.375
LUCCI'S THE FINGER DOWN
THE THROAT OF MY HAPPINESS.

11:49.458 --> 11:50.918
- WELL, SUIT YOURSELF.

11:51.001 --> 11:52.294
HEY, ELKA, CAN YOU DRIVE
SO I CAN FINISH THESE?

11:52.378 --> 11:55.381
- OH, SURE.

11:56.715 --> 11:59.009
- VICTORIA?
- [gasps]

11:59.093 --> 12:02.596
HOW DO YOU JUST
APPEAR LIKE THAT?

12:02.680 --> 12:05.182
- ARE YOU OKAY?
YOU SEEM A LITTLE TENSE.

12:05.266 --> 12:07.685
- WELL,
OF COURSE I'M TENSE.

12:07.768 --> 12:11.313
I KNOW YOU'RE UP TO SOMETHING,
AND IT'S DRIVING ME CRAZY.

12:11.397 --> 12:13.816
IT'S LIKE ONE OF THOSE MOVIES
WHERE THE YOUNG INGENUE

12:13.899 --> 12:18.154
SUSPECTS THAT THE HIDEOUS CRONE
HAS A KNIFE BEHIND HER BACK.

12:18.237 --> 12:19.113
WAIT A MINUTE!

12:19.196 --> 12:21.991
YOU DO HAVE SOMETHING
BEHIND YOUR BACK!

12:22.074 --> 12:23.659
OH, THAT MEANS
THAT I'M THE YOUNG INGENUE.

12:23.742 --> 12:24.827
ALL RIGHT,
LET ME HAVE THAT!

12:24.910 --> 12:26.787
- NO, STOP! STOP!

12:26.871 --> 12:29.165
- AH! HA-HA!

12:29.248 --> 12:32.209
OH...IT'S AN EXQUISITELY
CRAFTED SCRIPT COVER

12:32.293 --> 12:34.295
WITH MY NAME
EMBOSSED ON IT.

12:34.378 --> 12:37.798
- IT'S YOUR MOVIE SCRIPT.
I WANTED TO WRAP IT FIRST.

12:37.882 --> 12:41.510
- OH.

12:41.594 --> 12:45.681
- VICTORIA, I REALLY AM JUST
TRYING TO BE A BETTER PERSON.

12:45.764 --> 12:47.683
I KNOW I HAVE
A LONG WAY TO GO, BUT...

12:47.766 --> 12:49.852
BABY STEPS.

12:49.935 --> 12:51.145
- WELL, WITH THOSE
LITTLE BABY FEET,

12:51.228 --> 12:54.940
WHAT ELSE COULD YOU TAKE?

12:55.024 --> 12:58.235
WELL, THERE IS
A SLIGHT POSSIBILITY

12:58.319 --> 13:00.529
THAT I MAY HAVE
MISJUDGED YOU.

13:00.613 --> 13:04.033
- I REALLY AM HERE
BECAUSE YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE

13:04.116 --> 13:06.577
WHO CAN UNDERSTAND
WHAT I'M GOING THROUGH.

13:06.660 --> 13:08.662
- I SUPPOSE YOU'RE RIGHT.

13:08.746 --> 13:10.414
WHEN YOU'VE LIVED
IN THAT SOAP OPERA REALITY

13:10.498 --> 13:13.501
FOR AS LONG AS WE HAVE,
IT'S HARD TO GET USED TO...

13:13.584 --> 13:15.211
<i>REALITY</i> REALITY.

13:15.294 --> 13:18.172
- I DON'T LIKE
<i>REALITY</i> REALITY.

13:18.255 --> 13:21.008
IT'S TOO REAL.

13:21.091 --> 13:24.178
- IT'S TRAGIC, REALLY.

13:24.261 --> 13:27.556
WE'RE THE LAST OF
THE TRULY GREAT CULTURAL ICONS.

13:27.640 --> 13:33.354
- WITHOUT US, THE WORLD WILL BE
A FAR LESS DRAMATIC PLACE.

13:45.115 --> 13:47.910
- YOU'LL FIND THAT THIS IS
THE HARDEST PART OF REAL LIFE.

13:47.993 --> 13:51.747
YOU CAN'T NATURALLY FADE OUT
AND GO TO COMMERCIAL.

13:57.002 --> 13:58.420
- MMM.
- OH, GOD, IT'S...

13:58.504 --> 13:59.547
- MELANIE?

13:59.630 --> 14:02.758
[mouth full]
- HEY, DR. KAGEN.

14:02.841 --> 14:05.094
- WHEN YOU CAME INTO MY OFFICE,
YOU SAID YOU WERE FASTING

14:05.177 --> 14:06.428
FOR SOME BATHING SUIT TRIP.

14:06.512 --> 14:09.056
YOU'RE OBVIOUSLY
GOING WITH A ONE PIECE.

14:09.139 --> 14:11.767
- NO, ACTUALLY,
THE WEIGHT IS FALLING OFF ME!

14:11.850 --> 14:14.728
- ABOUT THAT,
IT'S LUCKY I RAN INTO YOU.

14:14.812 --> 14:15.980
I JUST GOT
YOUR TEST RESULTS.

14:16.063 --> 14:18.232
YOU NEED TO COME INTO THE OFFICE
FIRST THING TOMORROW MORNING.

14:18.315 --> 14:19.316
- WHY?

14:19.400 --> 14:21.151
OH, MY GOD.
AM--AM I SICK?

14:21.235 --> 14:22.278
- HAVE YOU
BEEN ABROAD LATELY?

14:22.361 --> 14:23.571
- NO.

14:23.654 --> 14:26.949
- EATEN ANY RANCID MEAT
OFF THE GROUND?

14:27.032 --> 14:28.909
- NO, OF COURSE NOT.

14:28.993 --> 14:30.661
I MEAN, I ATE A PANCAKE
THAT FELL ON THE FLOOR

14:30.744 --> 14:32.329
OF THE CAR, BUT IT'D
JUST BEEN DETAILED.

14:32.413 --> 14:35.082
- MELANIE...

14:35.165 --> 14:37.626
YOU HAVE A TAPEWORM.
- TAPEWORM?

14:37.710 --> 14:39.920
- IT'S BURIED ITS HOOKS
IN YOUR INTESTINAL WALL.

14:40.004 --> 14:42.006
THAT'S WHY
YOU'RE LOSING WEIGHT.

14:42.089 --> 14:44.133
- WELL, HOW BIG IS IT?

14:44.216 --> 14:46.260
- THEY CAN GROW
UP TO 50 FEET.

14:46.343 --> 14:51.223
- WE'RE GONNA NEED
SOME MORE FRIES.

14:52.725 --> 14:54.810
- OH! LET ME GET THAT.

14:54.893 --> 14:56.770
UNLESS YOU'RE ONE OF
THOSE MEN WHO'S UNCOMFORTABLE

14:56.854 --> 14:58.022
LETTING A WOMAN PAY.

14:58.105 --> 15:00.816
- NO, I'VE MADE
MY PEACE WITH THAT.

15:00.899 --> 15:03.444
- CLEVELAND VICE.
YOU'RE BOTH UNDER ARREST.

15:03.527 --> 15:04.862
- FOR WHAT?

15:04.945 --> 15:06.822
- SOLICITATION
AND PROSTITUTION.

15:06.905 --> 15:10.159
- HOW DARE YOU!
I AM NOT A PROSTITUTE.

15:10.242 --> 15:11.493
- OF COURSE NOT.

15:11.577 --> 15:12.995
- WELL, WHY DO YOU
SAY IT LIKE THAT?

15:13.078 --> 15:16.040
I MEAN, I COULD
BE A PROSTITUTE.

15:16.123 --> 15:19.501
{\an1}IS IT SO UNBELIEVABLE THAT A MAN
WOULD PAY TO HAVE SEX WITH ME?

15:19.585 --> 15:22.171
- MA'AM,
HE'S THE PROSTITUTE.

15:22.254 --> 15:23.172
- [laughs]
BUT HE CAN'T BE.

15:23.255 --> 15:25.466
HE'S SO SWEET AND GENTLE,

15:25.549 --> 15:28.677
AND ALL HE CARES ABOUT IN BED
IS IF I'M HAPPY.

15:28.761 --> 15:31.680
OHH.

15:31.764 --> 15:36.018
- I DO WANT TO OPEN
A WINERY THOUGH.

15:36.101 --> 15:38.520
- MELANIE!
I'VE BEEN LUCCI'D!

15:38.604 --> 15:40.356
- ME TOO!
SHE GAVE ME A PARASITE!

15:40.439 --> 15:43.359
- SHE GAVE ME
A PROSTITUTE!

15:45.569 --> 15:49.365
- MOMMY,
YOU FIRED NANNY BRIDGET?

15:49.448 --> 15:51.742
- YES, FOR HELPING YOU
HIDE THAT HIDEOUS PUPPY

15:51.825 --> 15:53.243
I TOLD YOU TO GET RID OF.

15:53.327 --> 15:56.246
- BUT RAGS
IS MY ONLY FRIEND.

15:56.330 --> 15:58.457
OH, YOU'RE RIGHT,
VICTORIA.

15:58.540 --> 16:00.334
SHE'S WRITTEN YOU
LIKE SOME KIND OF A MONSTER,

16:00.417 --> 16:03.545
WHICH YOU ARE SO NOT.
- WELL, THANK YOU.

16:03.629 --> 16:06.048
YOU KNOW, MAYBE
HONOR ST. RAVEN AND ERICA KANE

16:06.131 --> 16:10.052
COULDN'T BE FRIENDS,
BUT PERHAPS VICTORIA CHASE

16:10.135 --> 16:11.345
AND SUSAN LUCCI CAN.

16:11.428 --> 16:12.596
[door opens]

16:12.680 --> 16:14.682
- YOU BLOW-DRIED
LITTLE BITCH.

16:14.765 --> 16:17.226
- I KNEW IT!
WHAT DID SHE DO?

16:17.309 --> 16:18.560
- SHE GAVE ME A TAPEWORM!

16:18.644 --> 16:19.436
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
YOU'D BEEN TAKING

16:19.520 --> 16:21.563
THAT SUPPLEMENT FOR YEARS!
- I HAVE!

16:21.647 --> 16:23.065
LOOK AT ME.

16:23.148 --> 16:26.235
AT THIS POINT,
I'M MORE WORM THAN WOMAN.

16:26.318 --> 16:30.739
- MY PERFECT DOCTOR
TURNED OUT TO BE A MAN-WHORE.

16:30.823 --> 16:33.450
- ELKA...
ARE YOU MAD AT ME TOO?

16:33.534 --> 16:36.620
- JOY WAS ARRESTED,
MELANIE'S WORMY,

16:36.704 --> 16:37.579
THE CAVS ARE WINNING.

16:37.663 --> 16:41.083
I'M GOOD.

16:41.166 --> 16:43.377
- I CAN'T BELIEVE
I WAS THIS CLOSE

16:43.460 --> 16:44.420
TO BELIEVING
THAT YOU HAD CHANGED.

16:44.503 --> 16:47.047
HOW DARE YOU
LUCCI MY FRIENDS!

16:47.131 --> 16:50.259
- I WANTED THEM TO LIKE ME.
I GAVE THEM WHAT THEY NEEDED.

16:50.342 --> 16:52.970
- TAPEWORMS
AND PROSTITUTES?

16:53.053 --> 16:55.055
HOW DID YOU POSSIBLY
THINK THIS WOULD END?

16:55.139 --> 16:56.724
- I DON'T KNOW.

16:56.807 --> 17:01.478
AS ERICA KANE, I NEVER HAD
TO THINK MORE THAN A WEEK AHEAD.

17:01.562 --> 17:05.983
I'VE BECOME
MY OWN WORST NEMESIS.

17:06.066 --> 17:08.402
I'M MY OWN EVIL TWIN.

17:10.154 --> 17:12.781
[dramatic soap opera music]

17:12.865 --> 17:14.575
♪ ♪

17:14.657 --> 17:17.618
- HELLO?

17:17.703 --> 17:19.621
BARON!

17:19.704 --> 17:23.291
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
YOU'RE LEAVING THE TEAM?

17:23.375 --> 17:26.878
I'VE BEEN LUCCI'D!

17:26.962 --> 17:28.630
- [sobbing]

17:28.714 --> 17:31.341
- I CALLED YOU
A CAB TO THE AIRPORT.

17:31.425 --> 17:34.511
I'LL SEND YOUR AMERICAN
GIRL-SIZED CLOTHES ALONG LATER.

17:38.557 --> 17:41.935
MORE FAKE TEARS?
YOU ARE A DISGRACE TO NASA!

17:42.019 --> 17:43.854
WAIT...

17:46.231 --> 17:47.816
YOUR NOSE
IS ACTUALLY RUNNING?

17:47.900 --> 17:50.110
OH, MY GOD,
THOSE TEARS ARE REAL.

17:50.194 --> 17:51.236
- [muffled]
DON'T LOOK AT ME.

17:51.320 --> 17:53.489
- OH...

17:53.572 --> 17:55.699
THERE, THERE.

17:55.783 --> 18:00.204
JUST KEEP IT IN.
DON'T--DON'T LET IT OUT.

18:00.287 --> 18:02.456
- WHEN YOU PLAY
A CHARACTER FOR DECADES,

18:02.539 --> 18:05.334
IT JUST BECOMES
A PART OF YOU.

18:05.417 --> 18:09.046
IF I'M NOT ERICA KANE MARTIN
BRENT CUDAHY CHANDLER ROY ROY

18:09.129 --> 18:12.174
MONTGOMERY MONTGOMERY
MARRICK MARRICK MONTGOMERY,

18:12.257 --> 18:15.093
THEN WHO AM I?

18:15.177 --> 18:17.179
- I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

18:17.262 --> 18:19.348
WHEN I STOPPED PLAYING
HONOR ST. RAVEN VON KLAUS

18:19.431 --> 18:24.144
YOKOMOTO [clicks tongue]
ST. RAVEN, I FELT LOST.

18:24.228 --> 18:27.314
- IT'S JUST AWFUL, ISN'T IT?
- IT'S THE WORST.

18:27.397 --> 18:29.149
YOU KNOW,
IT'S BEEN THREE YEARS FOR ME,

18:29.233 --> 18:31.527
AND I STILL
MISS IT EVERY DAY.

18:31.610 --> 18:34.988
- BUT YOU'VE TOTALLY
REINVENTED YOURSELF.

18:35.072 --> 18:37.741
THAT'S WHY I CAME HERE.
TO SEE HOW YOU DID IT.

18:37.825 --> 18:41.203
- THAT WAS YOUR EVIL PLAN?
TO BE LIKE ME?

18:41.286 --> 18:42.871
- YES.
YOU HAVE A NEWS SHOW,

18:42.955 --> 18:45.582
COMMERCIALS, NOW YOU'RE
PLAYING YOURSELF IN A MOVIE.

18:45.666 --> 18:47.876
- N-NO, BUT THAT TOOK
TIME AND PERSEVERANCE

18:47.960 --> 18:50.003
TO RESTART MY CAREER.

18:50.087 --> 18:52.381
AND THIS MOVIE
MAY VERY WELL END IT AGAIN.

18:52.464 --> 18:55.217
- SO TELL THE PRODUCERS
THAT IF THEY DON'T MAKE YOU

18:55.300 --> 18:57.928
MORE SYMPATHETIC,
YOU'LL WALK.

18:58.011 --> 19:00.180
THERE'S NO MOVIE
WITHOUT YOU.

19:00.264 --> 19:04.351
THIS IS A STAR VEHICLE,
AND YOU ARE THE STAR.

19:04.434 --> 19:08.063
I SEE ANOTHER EMMY AWARD
IN YOUR FUTURE.

19:08.146 --> 19:10.858
- THANK YOU, SUSAN.

19:10.941 --> 19:14.403
I AM NOT DOING THIS MOVIE UNTIL
IT IS COMPLETELY REWRITTEN.

19:14.486 --> 19:17.865
- OH, THIS IS WONDERFUL.

19:17.948 --> 19:19.992
HOW ABOUT WE REALLY TRY
TO BE FRIENDS?

19:20.075 --> 19:23.287
- OKAY.

19:23.370 --> 19:26.415
UH...JUST TO BE SURE,

19:26.498 --> 19:29.084
YOU'RE NOT SMILING EVILLY
OFF INTO THE DISTANCE RIGHT NOW,

19:29.167 --> 19:30.419
ARE YOU?

19:30.502 --> 19:33.755
- OH, VICTORIA.
THIS IS REAL LIFE.

19:33.839 --> 19:36.884
- OH.

19:42.472 --> 19:45.100
- MOMMY,
YOU FIRED NANNY BRIDGET?

19:45.183 --> 19:48.478
- YES, FOR HELPING YOU
HIDE THAT HIDEOUS PUPPY

19:48.562 --> 19:50.105
I TOLD YOU TO GET RID OF.

19:50.188 --> 19:52.816
- BUT RAGS
IS MY ONLY FRIEND.

19:52.900 --> 19:55.277
- HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU?

19:55.360 --> 19:58.822
NO MORE
WIRE HAIR TERRIERS!

19:58.906 --> 20:01.825
[evil music]

20:01.909 --> 20:03.243
♪ ♪

20:03.327 --> 20:04.411
-<i> MOMMY MONSTROUS,</i>

20:04.494 --> 20:06.622
STARRING SUSAN LUCCI
AS VICTORIA CHASE,

20:06.705 --> 20:09.124
WILL RETURN AFTER THESE--

20:09.207 --> 20:13.503
- SHE REALLY CAPTURES YOU.

20:13.587 --> 20:14.963
- OH,
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

20:15.047 --> 20:16.965
THIS WAS
HER EVIL PLAN ALL ALONG,

20:17.049 --> 20:19.593
TO STUDY ME
AND STEAL MY PART.

20:19.676 --> 20:21.929
- I SWALLOWED A WORM.

20:22.012 --> 20:24.097
- WHEN THEY ASK
AT THE BLOOD BANK

20:24.181 --> 20:25.974
IF I'VE EVER HAD SEX
WITH A PROSTITUTE,

20:26.058 --> 20:30.520
I HAVE TO SAY YES NOW.

20:30.604 --> 20:34.024
- THERE, THERE, JOY.
